Point in time backups  snapshots   34 mins

commits reads the data from the staging area only.

working area  ------------ staging area -------------- commit area

when i issue a command git status
it will look into staging area.

I have 3 files file 1,file 2,file 3

git add file 1 

this file 1 file is moving from working area to staging area.

git ls-files
this commands gives how many files are there in staging area.

git show

it will show how many files are there in commit area.

git log

it will show how commts are done in this particular directory.

git log --oneline

git show commit id
git show head

